---
import ResourcesLayout from "@/layouts/ResourcesLayout.astro";
---

<ResourcesLayout
  title="Resources"
  activeMainText="Resources"
  activeSubText="Financial Resources"
>
  <main>
    <h1 class="heading">Financial Resources</h1>

    <h2>
      Welcome to the page that lists financial resources that are being
      assembled from around the state to help in these challenging times. These
      list a variety of resources for families that include food, clothing,
      housing assistance, legal/immigration help, domestic violence, and
      financial empowerment services that help with finding surer financial
      stability and footing.
      <br /><br />
      To find out more about these resources and the financial literacy pilot that
      is being developed for interested HFNY sites, please contact <a
        href="https://www.albany.edu/center-human-services-research/christine_callahan.shtml"
        style="color: darkcyan;">Dr. Christine Callahan at CHSR</a
      > at <a href="mailto:ccallahan@albany.edu">ccallahan@albany.edu</a>
    </h2>

    <img src="/images/frimage102020.jpg" alt="financial_resources" />
    <br /><br />
    <h2>Child Tax Credit - 2021</h2>
    <p>
      Check out <a
        href="/Documents/InfoontheChildTaxCreditforHFNYFamilies062021FINAL.pdf"
        >this document</a
      > for info on the expanded Child Tax Credit that can help HFNY families and
      bring more money into households this year.
    </p>

    <p class="instructions">
      Click on the links below for financial resources available in and around
      your location.
    </p>
    <div id="accordion">
      <h2 class="accordion-toggle">Capital Region</h2>
      <div class="accordion-content">
        <ul class="link-list">
          <li>
            <a
              href="/Staff/Documents/Financial_Resource_Guide_Schenectady_REVISED_1.28.2020.docx"
              style="color: darkcyan;">Schenectady Financial Resources Guide</a
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <h2 class="accordion-toggle">Mid-Hudson</h2>
      <div class="accordion-content">
        <ul class="link-list">
          <li>
            <a
              href="/Staff/Documents/Financial_Resource_Guide_Rockland_County2.11.2020.docx"
              style="color: darkcyan;"
            >
              Rockland County Financial Resources Guides</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a
              href="/Staff/Documents/Financial_Resource_Guide_Westchester_County9.1.2020.docx"
              style="color: darkcyan;"
              >Westchester County Financial Resources Guides</a
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <h2 class="accordion-toggle">New York City</h2>
      <div class="accordion-content">
        <ul class="link-list">
          <li>
            <a
              href="/Staff/Documents/RESOURCE_GUIDE_FOR_FINANCIAL_LITERACY_NYC_8.21.2019(revised).docx"
              style="color: darkcyan;"
              >Central Harlem Financial Resources Guide</a
            >
            <li>
              <a
                href="/Staff/Documents/NYC_Food_Pantrieslist.docx"
                style="color: darkcyan;">NYC Food Pantries</a
              >
            </li>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <h2 class="accordion-toggle">Central Western</h2>
      <div class="accordion-content">
        <ul class="link-list">
          <li>
            <a
              href="/Staff/Documents/Financial_Resource_Guide_for_Steuben_County_2.10.2020.docx"
              style="color: darkcyan;">Steuben Financial Resources Guide</a
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <script
    type="text/javascript"
    src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.7/jquery.min.js"
  ></script>
  <script type="text/javascript" src="../js/accordion.js"></script>
  <style>
    /* accordion styles ===================== */
    .accordion-toggle {
      color: #39c;
      text-decoration: underline;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .accordion-content {
      display: none;
      padding-bottom: 0;
    }
    .accordion-content.default {
      display: block;
    }
    .instructions {
      background-image: url(/images/template_images/instructions-icon.png);
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      position: left top;
      color: #1d809c;
      padding-left: 1.5em;
    }

    /* Timeline dates */
    .date-list dl {
      display: inline-block;
      clear: left;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
      margin-bottom: 1em;
      padding-bottom: 0.5em;
      min-height: 4em;
    }

    .date-list dt {
      font-size: 4em;
      color: #ccc;
      float: left;
      margin: 0 0.25em 0 0;
      padding: 0;
      line-height: 0.8em;
      position: relative;
    }

    .date-list dd {
      margin: 0 0 0 10em;
      line-height: 1.6em;
    }

    .disc {
      padding-left: 0.75em;
      background-image: url(/images/template_images/black-bullet.png);
      background-repeat: no-repeat;
      background-position: 0px 10px;
    }
  </style>
</ResourcesLayout>
